# Core Safety (vcon-ui)

- Never commit secrets or populated `.env*` values (Auth0, Firebase, Sentry, API keys, tokens).
- Never hardcode production URLs, credentials, tokens, or DSNs in app code.
- Keep API calls out of UI components; use `src/app/common/api-services/`.
- Add or modify endpoints via `src/app/config/api-config/appUrls.ts` and base config in `src/app/config/environments/environment.ts`.
- Do not create duplicate files like `* 2.tsx`; update existing modules.
- Preserve existing behavior unless explicitly requested (auth flow, routing, token refresh).
